The paper deals with algorithms and complexity issues related to self-assembly of tiles, which is a topic in discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and computational geometry (cs.CG). The paper also discusses the producibility of assemblies, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC) and computational biology (cs.SI). Finally, the paper presents results on the efficiency of algorithms, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
